msgid "OAF is now relatively stable. If the test fails, please disable ad filtering, proxy, acceleration, and other modules. If you are unsure which modules are conflicting, it is recommended to reset the device and then disable the acceleration module in the firewall for testing. If only some Apps are not working, you need to update the App feature library, as the filtering effect is related to the App feature library."
